trans-unit.source: Represents the container for multiple-document interface (MDI) child forms.
trans-unit.target: Representerer beholder for flere dokumenter grensesnittet (MDI) underordnede skjemaer.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan arves.

trans-unit.source: You should not create an MdiClient control.
trans-unit.target: Du kan ikke opprette en MdiClient-kontroll.

trans-unit.source: A form creates and uses the MdiClient when you set the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Form.IsMdiContainer%2A> property to `true`.
trans-unit.target: Et skjema oppretter og bruker MdiClient når du angir den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Form.IsMdiContainer%2A>egenskapen `true`.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Form.IsMdiContainer%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.MdiClient"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.MdiClient"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the background image displayed in the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.MdiClient"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir bakgrunnsbildet vises i den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.MdiClient"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Use the BackgroundImage property to get and set the background image of a form’s MDI client area.
trans-unit.target: Bruk BackgroundImage-egenskapen til å hente og angi bakgrunnsbildet for et skjema MDI klientområdet.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Drawing.Image"></xref> that represents the image to display in the background of the control.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Drawing.Image"> </xref> som representerer bildet som skal vises i bakgrunnen for kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: This property is not relevant to this class.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen gjelder ikke denne klassen.

trans-unit.source: Arranges the multiple-document interface (MDI) child forms within the MDI parent form.
trans-unit.target: Ordner flere dokumenter grensesnittet (MDI) underordnede skjemaer i skjemaet MDI overordnede.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Form.LayoutMdi%2A> method to arrange MDI child forms on a parent form.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Form.LayoutMdi%2A>metode for å ordne MDI underordnede skjemaer på et overordnet skjema.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Form.LayoutMdi%2A>

trans-unit.source: One of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.MdiLayout"></xref> values that defines the layout of MDI child forms.
trans-unit.target: Én av de <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.MdiLayout"> </xref> verdier som definerer oppsettet for underordnede MDI-skjemaer.

trans-unit.source: Gets the child multiple-document interface (MDI) forms of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.MdiClient"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Henter underordnet flere dokumenter grensesnittet (MDI)-typer i <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.MdiClient"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Form.MdiChildren%2A> property to get the child MDI forms of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MdiClient>.
trans-unit.target: Bruk <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Form.MdiChildren%2A>til å hente underordnet MDI typer <xref:System.Windows.Forms.MdiClient>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.MdiClient> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Form.MdiChildren%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Form"></xref> array that contains the child MDI forms of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.MdiClient"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Form"> </xref> matrise som inneholder skjemaene underordnede MDI av den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.MdiClient"> </xref>.
